Terms of Service Method of Payment: Paypal Money Order Check
Payment expected within 7 days of agreement to purchase. Email jjsbargains@gmail.com to advise when payment sent and if there are any delays. If there is no contact within 7 days item will be restocked and member will be banned from purchasing. Paying by Check? We will accept checks as long as it works out. There will be a waiting period once the check is recieved, until the check clears. We will charge a $25 fee for any bounced checks!
Shipping First class shipping added to all sales. Depends on size of item shipped. Email jjsbargains@gmail.com if you have any questions about shipping cost for a specific item. Insurance You must purchase insurance for all items over $20 for your safety as well as ours! Questions or Concerns? Email jjsbargains@gmail.com
